3c4d5e6f-3334-7678-9101-312131415163.description: During the tracking week ending February 22, 2025, the song debuted at #61 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart. During the tracking week ending June 7, 2025, the song reached a new peak of #1, giving him his first #1 on the chart.
